# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:261
msgid "Installing Inkscape"
msgstr "Menginstal Inkscape"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:263
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Advanced Editor` feature in the :guilabel:`Title Editor` "
"dialog requires the latest version of Inkscape (https://inkscape.org/"
"release/) be installed and the OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the "
"correct path to the Inkscape executable. See the :ref:"
"`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences."
msgstr ""
"Fitur :guilabel:`Advanced Editor` dalam dialog :guilabel:`Title Editor` "
"memerlukan versi terbaru Inkscape (https://inkscape.org/release/) yang "
"terinstal dan **Preferences** OpenShot diperbarui dengan jalur yang benar ke "
"executable Inkscape. Lihat tab :ref:`preferences_general_ref` di Preferences."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:270
msgid "Installing Blender"
msgstr "Menginstal Blender"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:272
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Animated Title` feature in OpenShot requires the latest "
"version of Blender (https://www.blender.org/download/) be installed and the "
"OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the correct path to the Blender "
"executable. See the :ref:`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences. NOTE: "
"The minimum supported version of Blender is 5.0+. Older versions of Blender "
"are not compatible with OpenShot Video Editor."
msgstr ""
"Fitur :guilabel:`Animated Title` di OpenShot memerlukan versi terbaru "
"Blender (https://www.blender.org/download/) yang terinstal dan "
"**Preferences** OpenShot diperbarui dengan jalur yang benar ke executable "
"Blender. Lihat tab :ref:`preferences_general_ref` di Preferences. CATATAN: "
"Versi minimum Blender yang didukung adalah 5.0+. Versi Blender yang lebih "
"lama tidak kompatibel dengan OpenShot Video Editor."

